Results.ReviewText: My girlfriend and I bought this coffee after sampling some on a plane journey! It has such a deep rich flavour and an immediate pick-me-up effect! Rarely a day goes by without a cup of Azera, either for when we are snuggled in front of the TV, or in the handy takeaway cups with swivel lid in the multipacks. Note. The only slight feedback I would give is, make sure you stir it well, as it can clump in the bottom of the mug. Otherwise, this is a cracking coffee!! :)
Results.Title: Does what it say's on the tin! ;)

Results.ReviewText: I think Nescafe hit the Jackpot with this coffee. It is by far the best coffee on the market at the minute. It is the closest coffee I have tasted that reflects freshly made coffee from a coffee shop. The aroma of Americano coffee is divine. I put the extra spoon of this coffee in my cup to get the maximum full flavoured aroma of the coffee. I like full bodied, rich aroma coffee and this has it in spades. I also love that crema effect when the hot water is poured. This appearance oozes freshness and aroma. Excellent coffee. Always have a spare tin in the cupboard. Always recommend this coffee to people.
Results.Title: Converted Azera Coffee drinker

Results.ReviewText:
I will actually add to this to make it a more substantial review.
My wife and I stumbled by accident on Azera a couple of years ago, and since then we haven't purchased any other brand of coffee. Azera tastes amazing its smooth but tastes like a freshly ground coffee. The fine granules make for a better coffee in my opinion. it is slightly more expensive than other brands but it's quality outweighs the price difference. plus opening a new tin of Azera is an experience in itself the aroma you get is second to none. Awesome!
Results.Title: one word "Awesome"

Results.ReviewText:
It's been a while since I tried this but the flavour was memorable for being slightly stronger than Nescafe original but with a much stronger aroma which gave an altogether more enjoyable drink. It's not too far to say it made drinking coffee an experience (a nice one at that) but the only downside is that the price reflects the exclusivity of the brand and so it's more often than not our of my budget. If you can afford it though it's well worth trying. 

In exchange for this honest and impartial review I am entered into a prize draw. This does not affect my stated views of the coffee.
Results.Title: Good balance with a gorgeous aroma

Results.ReviewText: I have being buying this coffee for months now , the nicest coffee I have ever tasted fell inlove with it from the first cup , it is smooth rich and delicious all wrapped into one, and the best thing is it is great value and the tin is very easy on the eye . Please keep up the good work nescafe.
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText:
I have tried many varieties of coffee, but many of them don't live up to expectations. The first time that I tried Azera, I was very surprised. The flavour is full and rich and very satisfying. It's a bit like a filter coffee without all the fuss.
I can heartily recommend Azera.
Results.Title: Full bodied flavour

Results.ReviewText: i tried this a while back and loved it instantly (pardon the pun). i always get a coffeee on the go - an americano is my choice. but having family stay over recently i purchased a tin of Azera americano and it went down a treat! everyone commented and asked what the coffee is.
Results.Title: a beautiful coffee anywhere and anytime.

Results.ReviewText:
I drink this coffee everyday and I love it
That first drink in the morning and the best start to any day ahead, amazing flavour and smoothness
I have pots of this coffee everywhere, work, at my mums and even have a small pot to pack away to take on any break - My favourtie
Results.Title: Smooth and tasty

Results.ReviewText: I am very fussy when it comes to coffee. I tried many different brands and types of coffee in the past and I can safely say that I settled with this one. I am on my third tin at the moment - love the smoothness, the full taste without bitterness, perfect blend for me.
Results.Title: Best one yet

Results.ReviewText: I love my coffee but even I found this strong I would normally have a strength of 3 but decided to kick it up a notch. Boy did this do it but too much for me but my other half loved it and nearly has it all gone. Will definitely buy it again just to make him happy.
Results.Title: Very strong!

Results.ReviewText: I love my coffee and most days I need it to keep going.  It is very hard to find a coffee that tastes great and works on my energy levels.  This Americano coffee is divine.  It is rich and delicious, and keeps me going for hours.  A winner for me hands down
Results.Title: Absolutely delicious

Results.ReviewText: My favourite Nescafe coffee! It tastes like a coffee you would buy from an expensive coffee shop from bean to cup. I love strong tasting coffee and this ticks all the boxes for me. It is strong, but smooth without the bitter taste. I love Azera Americano.
Results.Title: excellent ground coffee tasting

Results.ReviewText: I've always loved coffee but would never be fussy about what coffee I was drinking. Some of my friends started drinking this specific coffee and asked me to try it...I loved it as soon as I had one sip! It has an amazing taste and always buy this now!
Results.Title: Amazing smooth taste!

Results.ReviewText:
We have tried this coffee, Nescafe Azera Americano a few times now and can honestly say it is so flavoursome, full bodied and smooth, it takes some beating for taste compared to some others.
This is one of our favourites and excellent value.
Results.Title: Very tasty!

Results.ReviewText: First purchased this a couple of months ago having found that some other coffees seemed to taste of "cigarette ash" (not that I've ever tasted it!!!). However, this is a really smooth, slightly nutty tasting coffee that the whole family like.
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee a few months ago for my husband, I liked the look of the tin and decided to treat him.  He absolutely loves the coffee and tells me it is rich and full flavoured and smooth.  And the tin keeps the coffee lovely and fresh.
Results.Title: Husband is happy!

Results.ReviewText: Do not really drink coffee so when my friend offered me a cup of Azera i wasnt really keen. However it smelt lovely and it was a smooth velvety taste, she gave me a tin and now I have it at work, really love it, so had to do a review.
Results.Title: fantastic coffee

Results.ReviewText: As a professional Chef I'm always looking for ways to take an ingredient and change it into something else without losing the original flavour. The Azera Americano done just this when developing a frothy take on and American Egg Nog
Results.Title: Smooth, tasty & adaptable

Results.ReviewText: I have been able to convert my husband from tea to coffee since I first purchased Azera Americano. The very fine coffee powder dissolves instantly and the aroma and flavour are just what you would wanr from a good cup of coffee.
Results.Title: Very smooth coffee flavour

Results.ReviewText: My girlfriend and I are big coffee drinkers and sometimes when we are short of time, we use this instead of fussing about with our coffee machine. We are both very fussy when it comes to your coffee. We tried many different brands and types of coffee in the past and we agreed we had hit the jackpot when we 1st sipped our 1st cup using this blend and we have stopped our search . We love the smoothness, the full taste without bitterness, perfect blend for us.
Results.Title: The best instant coffee by far

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee having seen the advertisment for it. I was extremely impressed  with the quality and taste.. I was a girl who frequently went out for coffee in order to get the real coffee taste. now I dont have to leave the house as I can enjoy it any time of the day or night.
Results.Title: Why leave the house?

Results.ReviewText: I first tried Azera at a friend's house. My first thought was 'what's wrong with the old instant?' and 'why the designer container?'. Then I had the first sip or two... Aha, now I get it. Coffee shop quality without the need for a barista - very clever. But I still haven't figured out how you do it!!
Results.Title: from sceptic to convert

Results.ReviewText:
I bought  this Americano Coffee hoping the taste would be pleasing yet not expecting such a great Hit. This was the best choice of canned coffee I have ever experienced.
I also love all the the nice comments made from my friends when I make them a cup of Nescafe Americano.
Results.Title: awesome in a can

Results.ReviewText: Azera is the best store bought coffee on the market. It's got a lite cream top to it upon adding water & topping it off with a drop of milk is like adding the cherry on a cake.  I keep can in the office, at home & at my partners.
Results.Title: Best nicest coffee on the market

Results.ReviewText: This is my favourite Nescafe coffee.  Starting with the gorgeous aroma when you pop open the tin right through to the rich smooth flavour when it's in my mug.  Don't think I'd get through my day without at least one cup!
Results.Title: Morning wake up call

Results.ReviewText: I've been drinking Azera for a few years now and can't praise the Americano enough.  It's like having a Starbucks in your kitchen.  Straight edge black no sugar is just amazing compared to any other similar product.
Results.Title: Real Barista flavours

Results.ReviewText: This is the best tasting instant coffee i have ever bought. I use a heaped teaspoon per cup and i get a lovely rich tasty cuppa. Usually i like to buy coffee out but this is the best for when i am at home or work.
Results.Title: Great tasting coffee

Results.ReviewText: I first started drinking Azera when there was only one option. I loved it, and bought my own for work instead of the naff instant coffee they gave us free. This is my go to instant coffee and I really enjoy it.
Results.Title: Best instant coffee I've found!

Results.ReviewText: I love this coffee. I had thought about buying a coffee machine, but was reluctant because they are too big to have at home. No need to even think about it now Nescafé have this fantastic range of coffees.
Results.Title: No need for a coffee machine!

Results.ReviewText: I bought this yesterday, It was really tasty, I felt like having it again and again . I would definetly recommend this to my friends.. THIS IS REALLY GOOD..and finally try and make more in future..
Results.Title: Really Delicious!!

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
Results.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD BLEND Instant Coffee
